Test Plan for "Rent a Car" Functionality

Objective:
The objective of this test plan is to ensure that the "Rent a Car" functionality of the system performs
as expected, meeting rider requirements and providing a seamless experience for riders.

Scope:
The scope of testing includes:

Rental booking process
Availability of cars
Pricing and payment
User authentication and authorization
Reservation management

Test Approach:
Functional Testing:

Verify that users can search for available cars based on location, date, time, and other filters.
Confirm the correctness of the displayed car details (e.g.Driver info, make, model, features, availability).
Ensure users can select a car, specify rental duration, and proceed to booking.
Validate the payment process, including different payment methods.
Verify that confirmation emails or receipts are sent upon successful booking.